From: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
Date: Wed, 27 May 2020 13:53:09 +0200
Subject: iommu/amd: Consolidate domain allocation/freeing
Git-commit: 301441a0994689b56e98a0e8ecdc383b144ed258
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: bsc#1175713

Merge the allocation code paths of DMA and UNMANAGED domains and
remove code duplication.

